  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Brazil Cerrado Climate Change Mitigation Single Donor Trust Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The program aims to reduce the rates of deforestation and make agriculture more sustainable. It will support registration of land  under the Rural Environmental Register to ensure compliance with the Brazilian Forest Code (requiring that a percentage of private rural land holdings are maintained with the native vegetation); provide technical assistance on sustainable agricultural practices and natural resource management, which is also an incentive to participate; and support measures to prevent and deal with forest fires.</narrative>
  </description>
